data.description: Come check out this cute cottage that resides in the Highlands neighborhood in its own cul-de-sac. No concerns of thru traffic and plenty of parking available with this lot location. A BRAND NEW roof was just installed to assist the next owner in obtaining the best insurance rates possible. This property was build in 2005 so it is already up to the post hurricane Ivan building codes which also helps with insurance rates. As you walk through the front door your kitchen will be to the right which boasts stainless steel appliances, gorgeous backsplash and natural wood like cabinetry that brings it all together. From the kitchen sink you can over look into the large living room with wood laminate flooring and plenty of natural light from the back sliding door. The split floor plan has the master bedroom on the south side of the home and the two spare bedrooms on the north side. This home has been meticulously cared for. Schedule your showing and see for yourself.
